                  <note>Occasionally, when the word God lines up, the scribe rubricates the first two and last three letters (e.g., 11v, 87v, 104v)</note>
                  <desc>Columetric layout of text:
                    <locus target="#105v #106r" facs="110">fols. 105v, 106r</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps148"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps148</span></ref>;
                    <locus target="#106v #107r" facs="111">106v, 107r</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2000Mazmur#Ps150"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT2000Mazmur#Ps150</span></ref>;
                    <locus target="#114v #115r #115v" facs="119 120">114v, 115r, 115v</locus> <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1566hababa#ThreeYouths3"><span xmlns="" class="w3-tag w3-red">No item: LIT1566hababa#ThreeYouths3</span></ref></desc>
